# Instructions:
# 1. Get your OpenAI API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# 2. Replace 'your-openai-api-key-here' with your actual API key
# 3. For enhanced tax research, get a Tavily API key from: https://tavily.com
# 4. Get your Vercel Blob token from: https://vercel.com/dashboard/stores
# 5. Replace 'your-vercel-blob-token-here' with your actual Blob token
# 6. Save this file as .env in your project root
# 7. Restart your server: npm run server
